title: Loan – new debitor
text: Client needs a new debitor under Loan Log into the POS Functions etc. -> Create debitor Fill in the needed fields -> Accept Click on the screen to go back to the login screen. Log into POS Scan the item the customer wants to borrow. Click Go to Payment Click Alternate Payment -> Loan Locate customer -> click Accept A loan receipt is now printed for the customer to sign.
description:
Client needs a new debitor under Loan 

  

  1. Log into the POS 

  

  1. Functions  etc. -> Create debitor 

  

  

 

  

  1. Fill in the needed fields -> Accept 

  

 

  

 

  

  1. Click on the screen to go back to the login screen. 

  

  1. Log into POS 

  

  1. Scan the item the customer wants to borrow. 

  

  1. Click Go to Payment 

  

 

  

  1. Click Alternate Payment -> Loan 

  

 

  

  1. Locate customer -> click Accept 

  

 

  

A loan receipt is now printed for the customer to sign.

title: Loan - remove after return (defective barcode)
text: If the barcode does not work (could be bad printing), you can still remove loans again. Log into POS Shortcuts Report Choose to and from dates Tick Print Journal to Screen Click Loan Choose Note Number Close and log back into the POS Click Shortcuts Click Search Note Enter the number and click the green button Click Reprint This reprints the loan note. You can now scan it and cancel it.
description:
If the barcode does not work (could be bad printing), you can still remove loans again. 

  

  1. Log into POS 

  1. Shortcuts 

  1. Report 

 

  

  1. Choose to and from dates 

  1. Tick Print Journal to Screen 

  1. Click Loan 

  

 

  

  1. Choose Note Number 

  

 

  

  1. Close and log back into the POS 

  1. Click Shortcuts 

  1. Click Search Note 

  

 

  

  1. Enter the number and click the green button 

  

 

  

  1. Click Reprint 

  

 

  

This reprints the loan note. You can now scan it and cancel it.
